@startuml
[*] --> GreetUser : user arrives
GreetUser : entry / nil
GreetUser : do / greet user / InsertCard
GreetUser : exit / user inserts card

InsertCard : entry / user inserts card
InsertCard : do / check PIN / CheckPIN
InsertCard : exit / PIN is correct or incorrect

CheckPIN : entry / user enters PIN
CheckPIN : do / check PIN / TryAgain
CheckPIN : exit / PIN is correct or incorrect

TryAgain : entry / user tries again
TryAgain : do / check PIN / KeepCard
TryAgain : exit / PIN is correct or incorrect

KeepCard : entry / user tries again too many times
KeepCard : do / keep card for security / ReturnCard
KeepCard : exit / card is kept for security

ReturnCard : entry / user cancels operation
ReturnCard : do / return card / DisplayOptions
ReturnCard : exit / card is returned

DisplayOptions : entry / user selects option
DisplayOptions : do / display options / ProcessRequest
DisplayOptions : exit / user selects option

ProcessRequest : entry / user makes choice
ProcessRequest : do / process request / [*]
ProcessRequest : exit / request is processed

GreetUser --> InsertCard
InsertCard --> CheckPIN
CheckPIN --> TryAgain
TryAgain --> KeepCard
KeepCard --> ReturnCard
ReturnCard --> DisplayOptions
DisplayOptions --> ProcessRequest
ProcessRequest --> [*]
@enduml
